Everyone begins watching.

You talk to the others and share theories on what this new life will be like. Most of the reincarnations are quite happy to be there, but some seem to be a little more fidgety. They want to be on that screen and living life over again. The ones who are happy to be there gladly share their opinions on the situation. They think the new you will have learned a few things and through instinct will know what mistakes to avoid. These ideas are thrown around until the new life begins on the screen. Everyone begins watching.

They want to be on that screen and living life over again. The ones who are happy to be there gladly share their opinions on the situation. They think the new you will have learned a few things and through instinct will know what mistakes to avoid. These ideas are thrown around until the new life begins on the screen. Everyone begins watching.

Everyone begins watching.
